data.description: Beautifully updated and well-maintained home with tons of living space. Large open floor plan throughout, spacious kitchen with a large center island and loads of cabinets for storage. Large walk-in closets in all of the bedrooms. HVAC- 2019, Roof- 2016, Water softener- 2017, water heater- 2020, appliances-2022, Back deck- 2019, fence- 2020. Exterior paint, newer lighting throughout, and landscaping 2023. This 3 br 2.5 ba home with a large loft is move-in ready with everything you could want. Massive master suite with a separate shower and garden tub. The neighborhood offers community parks, playgrounds, and a pool for all of the kids. Situated on a private cul-de-sac.
